<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Scheduled for Deletion</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 32px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }
    .email-header {
      background-color: #dc2626;
      padding: 28px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .email-body {
      padding: 32px 24px;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #374151;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #fef2f2;
      border: 2px solid #dc2626;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .info-box .label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .info-box .date {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #dc2626;
    }
    .cancel-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    .warning-box {
      background-color: #fffbeb;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #92400e;
    }
    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Account Deletion Scheduled</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p class="greeting">Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>We have received a request to permanently delete your IT Job Portal account. Your account will be deleted on:</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="label">Scheduled Deletion Date</div>
        <div class="date">{{scheduledDeletionAt}}</div>
      </div>

      <p>If you changed your mind, you can cancel this request before the date above by clicking the button below:</p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{cancelUrl}}" class="cancel-btn">Cancel Deletion</a>
      </div>

      <div class="warning-box">
        <strong>What will be deleted:</strong>
        <ul style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px;">
          <li>Your account and all personal information</li>
          <li>Your CV profile</li>
          <li>Your chat history</li>
          <li>Your job subscriptions</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0;">Note: Your job applications will be anonymised, not deleted, to preserve the hiring process for companies.</p>
      </div>

      <p>If you did not make this request, please <a href="{{cancelUrl}}" style="color: #2563eb;">cancel immediately</a> and consider changing your password.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      &copy; {{currentYear}} IT Job Portal. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
